# __NPM_NAME__

__DESCRIPTION_BLOCK__Built with the [fuz stack](https://www.fuz.dev/) from
[fuz_template](https://github.com/fuzdev/fuz_template): TypeScript,
[Svelte](https://github.com/sveltejs/svelte),
[SvelteKit](https://github.com/sveltejs/kit) with the static adapter,
[fuz_css](https://github.com/fuzdev/fuz_css),
[fuz_ui](https://github.com/fuzdev/fuz_ui),
and [Gro](https://github.com/fuzdev/gro).

## usage

```bash
npm i
npm run dev # or `gro dev`
```

## check

```bash
gro check # typecheck, test, lint, format check
```

## build

```bash
gro build
```

## deploy

Build, commit, and push to the `deploy` branch, e.g. for GitHub Pages:

```bash
gro deploy
```
